    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/2d3a5a86b10cb544b6fd2f0166a2d43f.avif?t=1765807273\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras_big/2d3a5a86b10cb544b6fd2f0166a2d43f.avif?t=1765807273 width=1600 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/74f410fddd7595e2cad9fab765c32373.poster.avif?t=1765807273\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/74f410fddd7595e2cad9fab765c32373.webm?t=1765807273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where <strong>code shapes the future</strong>, Typhon challenges you to build, fight, and adapt in a relentless tactical warzone. Step into the cockpit of your modular mech, <strong>script your victory</strong>, and evolve in real time against ever-changing threats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Typhon is not just a game. It’s a live simulation of survival, engineering, and battlefield dominance. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Code. Conquer. Evolve.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/0ffd5ceb05bf7533c84fae991e18d2df.avif?t=1765807273\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras_big/0ffd5ceb05bf7533c84fae991e18d2df.avif?t=1765807273 width=1600 height=260 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/9de92b534e010a916d41bafea4141fab.poster.avif?t=1765807273\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/9de92b534e010a916d41bafea4141fab.webm?t=1765807273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your missions unfold on the surface of <strong>AEGIS IVb, </strong>a distant alien world laced with ancient ruins, dangerous anomalies, and strategic value. Here, advanced machines battle for control in a high-stakes arena where every decision matters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From <strong>thermal zones</strong> to <strong>abandoned outposts</strong>, each environment challenges your tactical awareness and engineering skill. Whether you dominate through power, precision, or planning, <strong>Typhon rewards those who adapt</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/0076817da4f5bc0fb15e2240a7d3de81.avif?t=1765807273\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras_big/0076817da4f5bc0fb15e2240a7d3de81.avif?t=1765807273 width=1600 height=260 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/49a6d099ab24300b86e359fe83b9809f.poster.avif?t=1765807273\" width=720 height=405 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/49a6d099ab24300b86e359fe83b9809f.webm?t=1765807273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Typhon is a tactical sandbox built entirely in <strong>Python</strong>, where code is part of the battlefield. Every unit, behavior, and system are written in a language designed for clarity, flexibility, and full player control. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your army from the ground up, customizing loadouts and combat modules to face the shifting challenges of <strong>thermal zones, abandoned outposts, and reactive terrain</strong>. But beyond tactics and terrain, the real advantage lies in your ability to understand and modify the logic that drives it all. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Typhon, you don’t just play the game, you read it, shape it, and master it through code. <br> <strong>This is strategy, survival, and Python working together in real time.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/1158e5f25bfb19a7260dd9e1d7f1f276.avif?t=1765807273\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras_big/1158e5f25bfb19a7260dd9e1d7f1f276.avif?t=1765807273 width=1600 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/0f7c617cea78c0a8f2ec0fdb78febace.poster.avif?t=1765807273\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/0f7c617cea78c0a8f2ec0fdb78febace.webm?t=1765807273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mech is a fully customizable extension of your tactical mind. Every component you choose shapes how you fight, move, and survive. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons</strong> to dominate at range or in brutal close-quarters encounters </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mobility systems</strong> to traverse harsh terrain and reposition with precision </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sensors</strong> to enhance targeting, tracking, or environmental awareness </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power cores</strong> to fuel endurance, defense, and advanced systems </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Success on Typhon is about designing smarter, adapting faster, and turning code into combat power. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362580/extras/5b34ceff3ce17ea0434b29b18c779a74.avif?t=1765807273\" width=1600 height=766 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become part of a growing tactical mech strategist community. Share your code, discuss strategies, and get real-time updates directly from the developers. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord: Chat live with the dev team and fellow players, participate in events, and get exclusive Alpha access info. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Facebook: Follow us for news, developer blogs, and community highlights. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reddit: Engage in deep strategy discussions, share your custom mech builds, and connect with passionate coders. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay Connected with Developer Updates and Behind-the-Scenes Content  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
